Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:52.06,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}假面的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭  是我們學校的學生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了嗎  真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這個世界裡時間沒有動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真是悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}入此門者  當拋棄一切希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:03:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎各位同學來到小生廣原雪子擔當部長的考現學部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考現學就是以現代社會的森羅萬象為對象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做調查  研究的學問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說就是考古學的現代版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我已經聽了好幾遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  考現學部終於盼來了新部員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是兩名女生和一名男生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的  姐姐在七年前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤夜裡看到的肯定是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡思亂想太多比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經和大家聚到一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興啊  認識了好多夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子真厲害啊  在赤夜中一個人生存下來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  雪子也有特別的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一生氣就很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子總是這麼活潑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為也就只有這點優點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  在哪跟誰打架能傷成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的出勤快不夠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總是曠課  還想不想升學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  你這嫁不出去的缺男人婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久  你的對女性不出手主義讓我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  給我站住賢久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士稱呼我們為「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要回答即將消失的「碎片」們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及「碎片」還有幾人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還知道一個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤夜剛開始那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被個好像正義的夥伴一樣的人救了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同學  你也認識她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「她」  是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說得出口啊  那個世界的事  還有這能力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  決定了  今天的活動就是尋找那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然決定了那就事不宜遲  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久  逃哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然撞進來幹什麼  太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是正義的夥伴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡妹  又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學  搜查活動結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人吃驚啊  能看到黑月的人竟然有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像叫皐月來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什麼能力都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你這樣還能活到今天啊  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣嘛  我是在誇獎你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來點薯條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣啊  誰也不清楚赤夜的詳細情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  田島賢久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不進考現學部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越弱的狗就越想聚到一窩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田島賢久  對團體沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說我們是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赤夜再臨的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會自己想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒禮貌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  看起來雖然是那樣  不過他是個挺溫柔的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會噁心呢  反而會讓大家感到羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅前輩  亂打一通是贏不了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是急躁刀路就會越亂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為何而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護結花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是嘴上功夫  身體卻跟不上來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的感情沒有轉換成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你握著的劍寄宿著覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟就是達到悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的感情還沒有達到悟的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要訓練的不是身體而是心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將感情轉換成力量  只需要考慮這點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將感情轉換成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到力量  能保護結花的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說出來很尷尬  不過剛才要是在戰鬥中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說保護結花  驅前輩都已經死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了試試驅的覺悟  我本想對她攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他的動作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  結花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我還是弱得很丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一定會保護好結花的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強  我也一樣沒有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要驅君能在我身邊就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這也是為了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保護結花  想把這份感情轉換成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey ciao,buongiorno shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}你好  早上好  小栞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Piacere,come sta shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}很高興見到你  小栞你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quanto costa？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你別用這種讓人不堪入耳的義大利語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想跟拉丁的熱血沸騰的歸國子女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一場火熱的雙語戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你燒盡吧  燒成灰為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,capito
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}噢  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小栞  在歐美是女士優先的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都願意聽你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請順著這條路一直往前走  在右轉的地方去死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}卡波那拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}註：一種美食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arrivederci  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,325)\fs21}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個超級笨蛋  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再笨下去我都不知道該說他什麼笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花已經先過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅同學  有關昨天的修行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  現在正好在做考現學的實際操作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考現學的  實際操作？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  探索為什麼結花明明是幼兒體型胸部卻這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不下垂也不上挺  不用塑形胸罩就這樣還真是現代奇跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在神聖的學園裡幹這種羞人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  雪子  住手  快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是賢久前輩在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我燒成灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久前輩是念力點火能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrokineticist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}操焰者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」們  今夜不會失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對即將變為殘骸的罪人們  我沒什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無話好說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同學  他們倆拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉋切長光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  是用拳法的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快  草壁前輩被壓制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  阿瓦利提亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能打倒古拉  這些「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須擔心  這次由伊拉和因威迪亞上陣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有我斯佩爾比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  前輩怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩  不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我有力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想力量並非所有人都是期望得到才得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫去獲取力量  我就是這種境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…雪子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這神速…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的戰鬥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個小丫頭  敢小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿就像換了個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因威迪亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為「碎片」的處置交給伊拉就足夠了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我統統去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的夥伴  登場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉…竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤夜要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這代價很重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見的時候  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  結花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅…驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  明明受了那麼重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一摘下眼鏡就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重人格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人般的戰鬥能力和強勁的殺氣  那是在哪學到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  我不太想說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  雪子  你的傷沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我會再生的  天生死不了的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我很噁心對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我習慣了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始大家就都覺得我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生在德拉斯貝尼亞這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是戰亂和殺戮之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受我的人一共有四個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們各位  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會噁心呢  反而會讓大家感到羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就算受傷了也能立刻恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復成原來的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  結花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅前輩  美鈴前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:22:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待著你的入部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.57,0:24:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在惡夢的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.65,0:24:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有答案嗎
